## Rating Disagreement Rule

If an ECI rating is disputed, resolve the dispute by applying the disqualifier test.

If any disqualifier for the claimed level applies, the lower rating stands. No partial credit. No "nearly ECI-3" unless explicitly marked as informal transition language. No maturity claim may override a live disqualifier.

